title: UArts Masterclass Series: Conversation with Kenny Barron
description: Kenny Barron participates in an open forum at University of the Arts in Philadelphia. Kenny discusses his early experiences growing up in Philly, his distinguished career and his ideas about jazz education. The event was hosted by Don Glanden, Head of Graduate Jazz Studies. note: Kenny is off mic momentarily as he announces an opening solo piano selection. Interview begins at 9 minutes.
